FBIS3-4301 "drchi060_d_94020" FBIS-CHI-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 Northeast Asia ROK Foreign Minister To Visit Russia To Discuss DPRK SK2903115094 Seoul YONHAP in English 0846 GMT 29 Mar 94 SK2903115094 Seoul YONHAP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 29 (YONHAP) -- Foreign Minister Han Sung-chu will visit Russia in April to discuss the North Korean nuclear issue and President Kim Yong-sam's planned trip to Moscow. President Kim, who is currently in China, told the press over lunch Tuesday, "diplomacy with the four neighboring countries -- the United States, Japan, China and Russia -- is important in solving the North Korean nuclear problem, so I will send Foreign Minister Han to Russia in April."
